### ====================================================
### Elasticsearch Admin via Ingress
### URL: https://elasticsearch.dealtogether.ca
### Auth: admin / paytogether2026
### ====================================================

@elasticsearch_url = https://elasticsearch.dealtogether.ca
@username = admin
@password = paytogether2026

### 1. Vérifier la connexion Elasticsearch
GET {{elasticsearch_url}}
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}

### 2. Obtenir les informations du cluster
GET {{elasticsearch_url}}/_cluster/health?pretty
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}

### 3. Lister tous les index
GET {{elasticsearch_url}}/_cat/indices?v
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}

### 4. Voir le mapping de l'index 'deals'
GET {{elasticsearch_url}}/deals/_mapping?pretty
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}

### 5. Compter les documents dans l'index 'deals'
GET {{elasticsearch_url}}/deals/_count
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}

### 6. Voir tous les documents de l'index 'deals'
GET {{elasticsearch_url}}/deals/_search?pretty
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}

### 7. Rechercher dans l'index 'deals' par titre
GET {{elasticsearch_url}}/deals/_search?q=titre:Deal&pretty
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}

### 8. 🗑️ Supprimer l'index 'deals' (⚠️ ATTENTION)
DELETE {{elasticsearch_url}}/deals
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}

### 9. 🗑️ Supprimer un document spécifique par ID
DELETE {{elasticsearch_url}}/deals/_doc/8d5a6631-4c41-48e6-aad5-22e9fec1a5e7
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}

### 10. Voir les statistiques de l'index 'deals'
GET {{elasticsearch_url}}/deals/_stats?pretty
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}

### 11. Rafraîchir l'index 'deals' (rendre les changements visibles immédiatement)
POST {{elasticsearch_url}}/deals/_refresh
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}

### 12. 🗑️ Supprimer tous les documents de l'index 'deals' (sans supprimer l'index)
POST {{elasticsearch_url}}/deals/_delete_by_query
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": {
    "match_all": {}
  }
}

